			</div>
					<p class="recipe-card-summary no-print">If you&#8217;re looking for the perfect BBQ side dish, these crispy garlic parmesan potatoes are it. Golden baby potatoes, coated in a garlicky parmesan crust and roasted until deeply crispy. They&#8217;re ready in 40 minutes and honestly impossible to stop eating.</p>
		
                


		<div class="recipe-card-heading">

